<br>
Having a /drop command will allow us to drop the item to the floor that is being held at cursor, same as if we clicked into empty space.<br>
<br>
Times when dropping rods is extremely hard:<br>
MOBs are very big<br>
Corpse of a MOB nearby<br>
Ring events (too many people to find a drop spot)<br>
Pet (anyone's) next to you<br>
Someone medding near you<br>
<br>
Opening trade window is awful, hitting cancel then puts the mod rod somewhere in the inventory and you have to look for it when someone really needs it.<br>
<br>
Filling slots with bandages is very annoying to us with 35+ empty slots.  It's not a lot to ask for but will make our life so much more hassle-free.<br>
<br>
Verant:  Give us a /drop command!<br>
