Being a gnome I can shuffle rods in the middle of a big fight, squished in between the fat ogres and the backstabbing rogues. Only problem is people having trades on, so your last rod might go into a trade window with someone, but I keep an inventory slot open all the time for a rod, since I rod constantly with my Shield.<br>
